on></section></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">与天下大多数国家的古装剧一样，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">韩国的古装剧还原程度也十分堪忧</strong>。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">他们不仅把不同时期的李朝服饰都拍成李朝末年-大韩帝国时期的样子，甚至于直接等同于现代韩服，还毫不意外地加入了各种美化。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">由于韩剧的传播影响，我们对于韩服的印象基本都来自于这些韩国古装剧里的影视剧戏服。这导致了<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">很多人甚至对现代韩服本身都了解不多</strong>。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">胸口不顶蝴蝶结的现代韩服女装很多。男装也多是短上衣与裤子的搭配，而不是摇着扇子被帽檐遮住一半脸的欧巴。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">2005年，韩国承办APEC峰会时，拿出来的服饰叫<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“图鲁马吉”</strong>。对于很多中国网友而言，它就很陌生。实际上，它其实是<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">很常用的韩服外套</strong>。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="1.35875" data-src="https://3-im.guokr.com/jgi3vDvsq-v4b18v7oU9Yhr_Tu2BeVggzUCV4LyVBgUgAwAAPwQAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="800" style="vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://3-im.guokr.com/jgi3vDvsq-v4b18v7oU9Yhr_Tu2BeVggzUCV4LyVBgUgAwAAPwQAAEpQ.jpg?imageView2/1/w/555/h/754"></section></section><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(162, 161, 161);line-height: 1;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">2005年APEC峰会上，各国领导人穿的图鲁马吉</p></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 80%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="1.7770833" data-src="https://2-im.guokr.com/579ozvE-0ifn-SCeTAPGWWTjYkU139H935WctAfZQyngAQAAVQMAAEpQ.jpg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="480" style="vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;" src="https://2-im.guokr.com/579ozvE-0ifn-SCeTAPGWWTjYkU139H935WctAfZQyngAQAAVQMAAEpQ.jpg"></section></section><section style="text-align: center;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(162, 161, 161);line-height: 1;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">穿着韩服图鲁马吉的男女</p></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">这里其实又可以划分出两个“角色”，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">来自韩剧的李朝古装戏服和现代韩服</strong>。而且现代韩服还会和北朝鲜服饰作以区分。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">中国这端，<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">在明朝的整个历程里，明朝服饰本身也发生着变化</strong>。不过以本文的篇幅，已经经不起更复杂的“角色”区分了。既然明朝健在时的李朝时期服饰算作一个“角色”，那么，明朝也只能极不学术地算作一方“角色”了。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">另外便是现代汉服中仿制明代服饰的部分。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">现代汉服本身是一个比较庞杂且没人说得清的体系，所以，仿明汉服最多算现代汉服的子集（也有一些做仿明服饰的人并不认同自己属于现代汉服的一员）。又因为带了一个仿字，各自的仿制水平与仿制心态有差异，所以<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">仿明服饰自然也不能等同于明代服饰</strong>。</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;">以上这些“角色”之间的关系就可以来梳理一下了。虽然因为分类比较粗略，只能将一些特例忽略了——</p><p style="white-space: normal;box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section><section style="margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin-top: 20px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;align-self: flex-start;margin-right: 30px;margin-left: 30px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 20px;height: auto;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-3px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="font-size: 19px;color: rgb(68, 73, 85);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: no